    "description": "Are you a skilled Software Engineer looking for your next big career move? Zensar Technologies Asia Pacific Associates in Gwalior offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Zensar Technologies Asia Pacific Associates:\nZensar Technologies Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gwalior, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Zensar Technologies Asia Pacific Associates!",
